{"id": "1390406367994707988", "channel_id": "1389228108241960980", "type": 0, "author_id": "1207347087369568268", "author_name": "jpzr2323", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@&1166257943742787615> 能不能检查一下上面的bug给点反馈，小克已经够弱，修一下bug好不好。", "timestamp": "2025-07-03T18:58:30.631000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1389228108241960980", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.2.3.1 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881"}
{"id": "1390266656722259978", "channel_id": "1390266656722259978", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "目前我们关注到社区中，存在极少部分玩家利用「解包」手段，获取当前版本尚未实装的游戏内容信息，并进行传播。这些信息均为开发过程中的非正式信息随时可能修改，且此类信息的传播，可能影响到后续正式发布时其他守密人的正常游玩体验。\n\n    在此，我们呼吁大家请勿参与或传播通过解包获取的非正式信息。对于后续的解包和解包信息传播行为，我们将视实际情况，根据《使用许可和服务协议》及当地相关法律法规进行追责处理。\n\n    再次感谢守密人对《忘却前夜》喜爱，我们将尽一切努力继续为大家产出更多的优质内容！", "timestamp": "2025-07-03T09:43:20.868000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1390266656965656616", "filename": "1200-800.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 126407, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1390266656722259978/1390266656965656616/1200-800.jpg?ex=69cce8b8&is=69cb9738&hm=8f592aeaca67f6d70d00e32a7f11cc0ea02585f723b0ff9269f4a86d6ac84522&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1390266656722259978", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "禁止「解包」和「传播解包信息」行为的声明", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881"}
{"id": "1390266720697978990", "channel_id": "1390266656722259978", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**Statement Prohibiting \"Unpacking\" and \"Distributing Unpacked Information\"**\n\nCurrently, we have noticed that a very small number of players in the community are using \"data mining\" methods to obtain information about unreleased game content and subsequently spreading it. Please note that this information is unofficial and subject to change at any time as part of the development process. The spread of such information may negatively impact other players' experiences when the content is officially released.\n\n    Therefore, we urge everyone not to participate in or share unofficial information obtained through data mining. Regarding future acts of data mining and spreading related information, we will take appropriate actions based on the \"License and Service Agreement\" and local laws and regulations as necessary.\n\n    Thank you once again to all Investigators for your love and support for \"The Eve of Forgetting.\" We will continue to strive our best to bring you more high-quality content!", "timestamp": "2025-07-03T09:43:36.121000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1390266656722259978", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "禁止「解包」和「传播解包信息」行为的声明", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881"}
